articles.author: Samantha Mathewson
articles.title: A rare nova ignites a 'new star' in the sky this year. Here's how to see it - Space.com
articles.description: A nova outburst visible to the naked eye is expected to decorate the night sky this year, offering a once-in-a-lifetime stargazing opportunity.
